				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">/pet focus rocks -- I can even split mobs sometimes by knowing that the pet and I are burning down the same mob.
<br />

<br />
/pet focus also keeps pets from jumping targets when AoEs (or other damage) from another mob "confuse" them.
<br />

<br />

<br />
/pet no cast -- Jury is still out. I bought it so that mobs that flee at low health will do so even if I chose an earth pet. There is some early suggestions that it may boost total pet DPS somewhat.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.sovereignguild.org/forum/viewtopic.php?t=4429" target="_blank" class="postlink">Master Elementalist Itchyban of Veeshan</a>
