				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">If that's the case, let it be spoken of no more in any public forum SOE is known to frequent.
<br />

<br />
We all know what happens when they implement something that gives unintended benefits. This AA was fairly apparently only intended to prevent the earth pet from rooting mobs when the mage didn't want it to be casting root. 
<br />

<br />
Any DPS increase from the pet no longer wasting a good chunk of its time casting a spell that does a fraction of the melee dmg is an unintended side effect and will likely be nerfed if they find out.
<br />

<br />
Therefore, shhhhh.<br />_________________<br />Master Elementalist Sebboh Nivlac
<br />
