				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Sounds right Klotar. My habit on zoning into a combat zone these days is:
<br />

<br />
/pet hold (hotkeyed, as I use it quite a bit, especially raiding)
<br />
/pet focus (typed out)
<br />

<br />
/pet focus stays for the duration of time the pet in the zone. I don't recall if it "sticks" through suspend/unsuspend in the same zone though. (With the changes in invis not killing pets, I don't suspend too often in the same zone any more.)<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.sovereignguild.org/forum/viewtopic.php?t=4429" target="_blank" class="postlink">Master Elementalist Itchyban of Veeshan</a>
